    "steam_appid": 3212780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/6c4ac9f8209c0930600d0f48da3e4ed2.poster.avif?t=1748418562\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/6c4ac9f8209c0930600d0f48da3e4ed2.webm?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/6c4ac9f8209c0930600d0f48da3e4ed2.mp4?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示版内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此演示版可让您体验游戏的前 3 个章节。在第一个任务中与三个圣骑士团队见面，看看是什么引发了王国的政治动荡！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 CROWN GAMBIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Crown Gambit》是一款叙事战术游戏，你将在游戏中引导三位圣骑士踏上危机四伏的征途，穿过混乱不堪且政治动荡的首都。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宣誓效忠其中一位王位觊觎者，帮助其登上权力巅峰。忠于你自己的原则，但要小心谨慎，因为你的选择往往需要付出代价！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在阴谋家中选择一方，利用祖先圣物击败敌人，包括权力熏心的骑士、狡猾的贵族和反叛的平民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你愿意牺牲什么来拯救王国？你将拥护哪位王位继承人？王国的命运掌握在你的手中。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/c243e7debd4d51885650015aa5c3678e.poster.avif?t=1748418562\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/c243e7debd4d51885650015aa5c3678e.webm?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/c243e7debd4d51885650015aa5c3678e.mp4?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在混乱中开辟自己的道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场可怕的政治危机彻底动摇了米奥德雷德王国脆弱的权力平衡，与此同时，神秘力量似乎正在黑暗中操纵着一切。每位王位觊觎者都在集结军队以夺取王位，平民们则发动了叛乱，而潮水仍在上涨……在这场动荡的中心，你将扮演三位初出茅庐、手持圣物的皇家圣骑士，他们被迫做出艰难的抉择，以确保王国不会陷入混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在剧情当中做出艰难的选择来塑造圣骑士的个性，并始终坚持你自己的原则。明智地选择盟友，在竞争对手之间周旋以挫败阴谋诡计。但不要相信任何人：在混乱时期，欺骗才是至高法则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/77237875f8df772058e1b9159dc95564.poster.avif?t=1748418562\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/77237875f8df772058e1b9159dc95564.webm?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/77237875f8df772058e1b9159dc95564.mp4?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在震撼人心的卡牌战斗中感受十足的视觉冲击力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在近距离战术战斗中控制三位圣骑士：操控血液的侠盗艾丽莎、挥舞钉锤的牧师哈尔以及挥动船锚的肉盾罗洛。在使用圣物武器击溃敌人时，通过震撼人心的攻击动画，体验自己每一次重击的威力。时刻保持警惕，因为其他强大的圣骑士也在追随自己的誓言，他们不会不战而降。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中做好准备，仔细构建每位圣骑士的牌组，克服前进道路上的任何障碍。成为一支配合默契的团结战队，在与敌人的对抗中，让每一击都独具风格且至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/eed8cde0fd7ee02c2435d7a381118273.poster.avif?t=1748418562\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/eed8cde0fd7ee02c2435d7a381118273.webm?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/eed8cde0fd7ee02c2435d7a381118273.mp4?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>力量是一把双刃剑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过圣物引导黑暗而古老的力量，并召唤祖先恩典来扭转战局。你无疑将更快地消灭敌人，但要小心，因为获取这种神圣力量的代价很可能是你的灵魂……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/e88b0edd67245b25c56c88871d3f2ec4.poster.avif?t=1748418562\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/e88b0edd67245b25c56c88871d3f2ec4.webm?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212780/extras/e88b0edd67245b25c56c88871d3f2ec4.mp4?t=1748418562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>左右米奥德雷德的命运：</strong>请谨慎选择盟友和敌人，揭开众多曲折的剧情，包括多种结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扮演三位身陷这场政治混乱的无畏圣骑士并将三人组成一支战队：</strong>操控血液的侠盗艾丽莎、挥舞钉锤的牧师哈尔以及挥动船锚的肉盾罗洛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在回合制战术卡牌战斗中，迎战卑鄙的强盗、威武的骑士和恐怖的野兽</strong>，解锁毁灭性的技能，塑造每位圣骑士的战斗风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引导祖先恩典的黑暗力量</strong>，发动强大的攻击。但要小心：这股魔法的影响力可能比你想象的更难掌控。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越神秘的黑暗奇幻宇宙</strong>，沉浸在以凯尔特和布列塔尼民间传说为灵感的世界中，探索其中众多不可思议的奥秘。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欣赏由Gobert创作的大胆而富有表现力的手绘插画</strong>，以及融合了现代风格的令人难忘的中世纪配乐。</p></li></ul>",
